# Documentation
- [Setup](http://docs.rehborn.dev/cli/)
- [Usage](http://docs.rehborn.dev/cli/usage/)

# Setup

```shell
pipx install canary-cli
```

# Development

```shell
uv sync
canary-cli --install-completion
source $HOME/.bash_completions/canary-cli.sh
```

**Run with typer**
```shell
uv run typer ./canary_cli/main.py run 
```

### Linter
```shell
uv run ruff check
```

### Static Type Checker
```shell
uv run ty check
```
